{"tid":1956950,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"田中美奈實取代白石麻衣成寫真女王","createTime":"2020-04-03T14:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T14:15:46.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a088a119dc1457548971f9dabebfd24441ca29c","tid":1956950,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T14:02:18.000Z","msg":"33歲日本前女主播田中美奈實，轉行性感路線之後，去年12月推出處女寫真集《Sincerely yours...》銷量強勁，相隔5星期重返銷量榜冠軍，累積銷量已經有41.6萬本，取代女團乃木坂46主將白石麻衣大賣41.5萬本的寫真集《Passport》，成為Oricon寫真榜自2008年創辦以嚟最暢銷嘅寫真集。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200403/bkn-20200403162120193-0403_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200403%2Fbkn-20200403162120193-0403_00862_001.html&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2Bh9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=a2ac1b83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200403/bkn-20200403162120193-0403_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"00f6ae91a84a97e61d2d98fdda5e66faa5af363e","tid":1956950,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T14:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200403/photo/bkn-20200403162120193-0403_00862_001_02p.jpg?20200403163952\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200403162120193-0403_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20200403163952&h=7b8a8676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n田中美奈實寫真集銷量強勁，重登榜首。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200403/photo/bkn-20200403162120193-0403_00862_001_03p.jpg?20200403163952\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200403%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200403162120193-0403_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20200403163952&h=faafe351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n白石麻衣"},{"pid":"0186843a8b87019f9f131965b41898c66e146349","tid":1956950,"uid":262093,"like":2,"dislike":